prompt:
Extract all `action def` declarations from this SysML v2 model.

Return a JSON array where each object contains:
- "name": the action definition name
- "inputs": array of {"name": param name, "type": param type}
- "outputs": array of {"name": param name, "type": param type}

Example output format:
```json
[
  {
    "name": "ProvidePower",
    "inputs": [{"name": "fuelCmd", "type": "FuelCmd"}],
    "outputs": [{"name": "torque", "type": "Torque"}]
  }
]
```

Include ALL action definitions, even those without parameters.
